attributes.review: I was scrolling through TikTok and saw that ppl were talking about this app a lot and I mean A LOT so I decided to see what all the hype was about I was NOT pleased with what I got whatsoever the first thing the app did was ask for my number and I must admit I was kinda flattered so I decided to give it to them after that it asked for other personal info I got a lil scared at that point cuz I thought that it was tryna get info on me to take me out or som Idk🤷🏻‍♀️ I just gave them the info they needed and went on the app and much to my surprise the first this game I saw was a weird looking ORANGE 🍊 I must admit I was scared at first but I mean who can blame me 😞 it was 3am I thought my phone was being posed by a extremely WEIRD looking ORANGE after that I was scared and really tired so I decided to go to sleep and when I woke up I couldn’t believe my eyes .... my mom was standing next to me with a orange on her hand while saying Trump 2020 in a perfect American accent (she doesn’t know ANYTHING in English she only know Spanish) I was extremely worried about her so I asked her why she was saying that and she respond with “make America great again” I was really scared so I ran out and found my dog driving my dads truck and told me to hop in I was extremely confused but I decided to get in we drove out of the city and I asked princess what was wrong with my mom and you’ll never believe what she told me  😱😖 she said that sense yesterday at around 3am people started acting like our dear friend Donald and now the whole city were acting like crazy Karen’s and following every thing that the orange did IF YOU VALUE YOUR LIFE AND DO NOT WANT THIS TO HAPPEN TO THE PEOPLE YOU KNOW AMD LOVE I SUGGEST NOT TO GET THIS APP IT WILL RUIN YOUR LIFE!!!
